#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:2
#: 6b574ac8ee2d45afa50e2d80f3a933bd
msgid "工具说明"
msgstr "Tools"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:18
#: d14f49551fe946d98516ab0f01318b27
msgid "Dev Cube工具"
msgstr "Dev Cube Tool"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:21
#: 13f3f6333db240cd904551c7118a34d7
msgid "MCU和IOT这两个界面有什么不同的功能？"
msgstr "What are the different functions of the MCU and IOT interfaces?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:22
#: dbdb30924f894f78a890582ff366dad4
msgid ""
"MCU界面适用于MCU类芯片，搭配MCU SDK一起使用 IOT界面适用于带无线功能的芯片，搭"
"配IOT SDK一起使用"
msgstr ""
"The MCU interface is applicable to MCU-type chips and is used together with "
"the MCU SDK. The IOT interface is applicable to chips with wireless "
"functions and is used together with the IOT SDK."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:26
#: 75f83bbfc6204e0db421fcb5d806ab39
msgid "烧写时，可以自动选择flash嘛？"
msgstr "Can Flash be selected automatically during programming?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:27
#: 99074789af3848dd89493b506ea3a898
msgid ""
"烧写时，工具自动选择Flash，Flash选择优先级： 内封Flash Swap Pin > 内封FLash "
"> 外置Flash GPIO 17-22 > 外置Flash GPIO 0-2&20-22。"
msgstr ""
"During programming, the tool automatically selects the Flash. Flash "
"selection priority: internal Flash Swap Pin > internal Flash > external "
"Flash GPIO 17-22 > external Flash GPIO 0-2&20-22."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:31
#: 72c2dd09590e471abbf45fac2809f635
msgid "波特率最大可以达到多少？"
msgstr "What is the maximum baud rate?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:32
#: 94431f8535c54360920b67913db56058
msgid "工具使用UART烧写时，建议的最大波特率可以达到2000000。"
msgstr ""
"When the tool uses UART for programming, the recommended maximum baud rate "
"can reach 2000000."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:36
#: 8ec775621a1446a5a4c8ed617647e7e2
msgid "工具烧写1MB的文件，需要多久时间？"
msgstr "How long does it take for the tool to program a 1 MB file?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:37
#: 7567f7f7865b426cbbee6d09f5ebdf66
msgid ""
"工具选择UART下载，波特率2000000时，向Winbond Flash烧写1MB文件耗时11秒左右。 "
"该时间仅供参考，会因为Flash型号的不同有小幅变化。"
msgstr ""
"When the tool selects UART download and the baud rate is 2000000, "
"programming a 1 MB file to Winbond Flash takes about 11 seconds. This time "
"is for reference only and may vary slightly depending on the Flash model."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:41
#: e7a588f6a0de44638c1e8d96294eac62
msgid "下载失败的原因有哪些？"
msgstr "What are the reasons for download failure?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:42
#: 305cb3a59b41442a957eec82a148174a
msgid "芯片没有从UART启动，导致工具和芯片握手失败"
msgstr ""
"The chip does not boot from UART, causing the handshake between the tool and "
"the chip to fail."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:44
#: 0cbe9d0010ed4014b516cf8962b883c4
msgid "工具界面选择不合理，晶振选错等"
msgstr ""
"The tool interface is selected incorrectly, the crystal oscillator is "
"selected incorrectly, etc."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:46
#: f21d1b55af4947cea7d3fc660a5ac40d
msgid "烧写文件大小超过Flash可用容量"
msgstr "The programming file size exceeds the available Flash capacity."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:48
#: d6a13c5040ad4a5ba83e7ccb6314a486
msgid "使用外置Flash时，Flash有虚焊"
msgstr "When using external Flash, the Flash has a cold solder joint."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:50
#: 604a585254154a6398e5d66eb90ffda1
msgid "使用了工具暂不支持的Flash型号"
msgstr "A Flash model not currently supported by the tool is used."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:52
#: fbeb10214c58482ba9daef0759aeb7c8
msgid "Flash被写保护"
msgstr "The Flash is write-protected."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:54
#: 8665a742c4cf4f41bf4327dd7f3cbab3
msgid ""
"工具默认使用4线模式烧写Flash，有个别型号Flash最多只支持2线模式，这种情况需要"
"做特殊配置才能正常烧写"
msgstr ""
"The tool uses 4-line mode to program Flash by default. A few Flash models "
"support at most 2-line mode. In this case, special configuration is required "
"for normal programming."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:56
#: f9aee6a2572846a6b19e64c797ae8032
msgid ""
"工具log界面提示“Verify fail”，需要确认硬件板子设计是否能支持高波特率下载"
msgstr ""
"The tool log interface prompts \"Verify fail\". It is necessary to confirm "
"whether the hardware board design can support high-baud-rate downloading."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:60
#: 713fab0a1e444e388a8219722ac25cf9
msgid "使用说明"
msgstr "User Guide"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:61
#: 36ad3a8a5f5447ac96297e6a6ac630ed
msgid ""
"具体可参考《BLDevCube用户使用手册》。路径为：docs/BLDevCube用户使用手册.pdf。"
msgstr ""
"For details, refer to the \"BLDevCube User Manual\". Path: docs/BLDevCube用户"
"使用手册.pdf."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:64
#: 620890550e2246c8a13126fbb5bbc4f4
msgid "文件烧录进去后无反应，怎么排查问题？"
msgstr ""
"After the file is programmed, there is no response. How should the issue be "
"troubleshot?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:65
#: eacc0f2a0f264bd695a92774dd463b12
msgid ""
"在Dev Cube的IOT界面上是否勾选Partition Table(需要勾选)，是否选择了正确的分区"
"表文件(文件名不带boot2_iap，并与实际Flash大小匹配)；"
msgstr ""
"Check whether Partition Table is selected in the IOT interface of Dev Cube "
"(it needs to be selected), and whether the correct partition table file is "
"selected (the file name should not contain boot2_iap and should match the "
"actual Flash size);"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:67
#: 27c276f4d3244928ac75e38244b4ac0f
msgid ""
"在Dev Cube的IOT界面上是否勾选Boot2 Bin(bl602需要勾选，bl702不需要勾选)；"
msgstr ""
"Check whether Boot2 Bin is selected in the IOT interface of Dev Cube (bl602 "
"needs to be selected, bl702 does not need to be selected);"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:69
#: 6b39b935ea2b47f4873893adaad3924e
msgid "接上串口板，烧写其它能正常工作的bin文件(带有UART打印)，排除硬件问题；"
msgstr ""
"Connect a serial port board and program another bin file that works normally "
"(with UART printing) to rule out hardware issues;"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:71
#: 3481362e06a046eea8a647936a9728f7
msgid "是否修改了主函数名(bl602主函数为bfl_main，bl702主函数为bl702_main)；"
msgstr ""
"Check whether the main function name has been modified (the main function "
"for bl602 is bfl_main, and the main function for bl702 is bl702_main);"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:73
#: 92a79e2271774110b3fa2348e6c65154
msgid ""
"用FreedomStudio调试，是否能运行到主函数，不能的话，检查是否修改了portASM.S或"
"flash.ld；"
msgstr ""
"Use FreedomStudio for debugging. Check whether execution can reach the main "
"function. If not, check whether portASM.S or Flash.ld has been modified;"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:75
#: fdd524aac6ed432cb08a70786776b89a
msgid ""
"是否修改了UART初始化代码，是否将UART_TX引脚配置成了其它功能或配置成了高阻，"
"UART时钟是否被禁掉；"
msgstr ""
"Check whether the UART initialization code has been modified, whether the "
"UART_TX pin has been configured as another function or configured as high "
"impedance, and whether the UART clock has been disabled;"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:77
#: b295621528fc4f81b4814624a5ec4337
msgid "是否修改了printf函数或使用了其它打印函数；"
msgstr ""
"Check whether the printf function has been modified or another print "
"function is used;"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:79
#: c9a48b089d2a4c6e96510f4339ad1502
msgid "是否修改了系统时钟；"
msgstr "Check whether the system clock has been modified."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:83
#: 369146ba54f948ebbfd5eecb0cb5c198
msgid "Ai-WB2系列模组烧写是否需要接IO8引脚"
msgstr ""
"Does the Ai-WB2 series module need to connect the IO8 pin for programming?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:84
#: c67e791f87674c4884cf5ceb3a770efb
msgid "不需要，只需要接四根线，点击烧录软件的下载按钮后给模块硬件复位即可下载"
msgstr ""
"No. Only four wires need to be connected. After clicking the download button "
"in the programming software, reset the module hardware to start downloading."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:89
#: 9e05aa510b7e4af09d208fc1a7887501
msgid "工厂批量烧写工具"
msgstr "Factory Batch Programming Tool"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:92
#: a9f5fc64e67745b08fe85085585cf03e
msgid "批量烧写工具支持哪些烧写模式?"
msgstr "Which programming modes are supported by the batch programming tool?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:93
#: b6f66897442c452dbe3af23b68b54be3
msgid ""
"单文件模式： 工具界面指定烧写文件和指定烧写地址，工具会将指定文件烧写到Flash"
"指定地址上"
msgstr ""
"Single-file mode: Specify the programming file and programming address in "
"the tool interface, and the tool will program the specified file to the "
"specified address in Flash."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:95
#: 8ce568917cd84de4a044cbe5d09d82a7
msgid ""
"开发模式： 可以在配置文件中指定多个烧写文件和对应的烧写地址，工具会一次性烧写"
"多个文件到Flash对应的烧写地址上"
msgstr ""
"Development mode: Multiple programming files and corresponding programming "
"addresses can be specified in the configuration file, and the tool will "
"program multiple files to the corresponding Flash addresses at one time."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:97
#: f046b73d569d4552857b465c4b453f75
msgid ""
"动态模式： 支持动态生成烧写文件，适用于一机一码等烧写文件需要动态改变的场景，"
"动态文件生成功能需要按具体需求定制"
msgstr ""
"Dynamic mode: Supports dynamic generation of programming files. It is "
"suitable for scenarios where the programming file needs to change "
"dynamically, such as one device with one unique code. The dynamic file "
"generation function needs to be customized according to specific "
"requirements."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:101
#: b169a14fe44d40a4afcdff4b20f4c56c
msgid "批量烧写工具对于芯片上电时序有什么样的要求？"
msgstr ""
"What are the power-on timing requirements of the batch programming tool for "
"the chip?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:102
#: 3bd50ea948fd4ed28866a5c36a430cd7
msgid ""
"批量烧写工具在做烧写任务前，需要让芯片从UART启动。 建议使用博流烧写板控制芯片"
"的上电时序，确保批量生产时，烧写的稳定性。 博流烧写板和烧写工具之前会有一套软"
"硬件之间协同控制芯片上电时序的流程。"
msgstr ""
"Before performing a programming task, the batch programming tool needs to "
"make the chip boot from UART. It is recommended to use the Bouffalo Lab "
"programming board to control the chip power-on timing to ensure programming "
"stability during mass production. There is a set of software-hardware "
"cooperative processes between the Bouffalo Lab programming board and the "
"programming tool for controlling the chip power-on timing."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:107
#: bc6feafcb80e4ee8a681aa22035648ab
msgid "使用说明？"
msgstr "User Guide?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:108
#: dbda48be4f1143a2a3700b06098ceb4b
msgid "具体可参考《BL批量烧写工具使用手册》。"
msgstr "For details, refer to the \"BL Batch Programming Tool User Manual\"."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:111
#: 784d8b47db63437cbc933e18a54f3d08
msgid "请问WB2模组是否买了TTL模块就可以实现供电以及烧录功能？"
msgstr ""
"Can the WB2 module be powered and programmed after buying a TTL module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:112
#: 6b757e61ac1b4c78b7ae1a32bd7348e0
msgid ""
"是的，TTL `购买链接  <https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.3-c-s."
"w4002-24271435830.9.45c84853LqwXqs&id=565546260974>`__"
msgstr ""
"Yes. TTL `Purchase link  <https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.3-c-s."
"w4002-24271435830.9.45c84853LqwXqs&id=565546260974>`__"
